➜中介疯传契税上涨！确实，为卖房不择手段了
http://www.sohu.com/a/412732715_669315	18275
<p>有一种恶，叫一本正经的胡说八道。</p>
<h1><strong>1</strong></h1>
<p>一个多小时前，全网大量房产中介，都在转发一条消息：</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200812/685e5b7a876b4d3699be1b393946c734.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200812/db5acc59b39e4641a7dfaa7f1cb48380.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200812/fb1cc3657d664fcca885c12c20649263.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
